common_issues.title: Pieces desktop app issues on Windows and macOS
common_issues.description: Users reported issues with the Pieces desktop application on both Windows and macOS. On Windows, the copy button in the VS Code extension loads indefinitely. On macOS, the application periodically jumps to the main monitor and steals focus. Reinstallation and checking for extra processes may resolve the macOS issue.
